item.title: Rest Player (a ChatGPT plugin)
item.description: Rest Player A restful music player, allowing songs to be queued and played through HTTP calls. Can be used as a ChatGPT plugin Description Currently only compatible with Linux, this player makes use of the Python yt-dlp package to search for and stream songs from YouTube.
